metadata.name: Perpetual Movement
metadata.description:
Once it moves it will always move,
couldn't be stopped and continuously.

Everything moves by their own capacity.
No need to rush nor slowed down.

Every end is always a new starts.
No end and no beginning.

Universe moves and everything revolves following then movement.

We are the universe,
Everything moves by their own capacity.
No need to rush nor slowed down.

Know who you are, parts of the massive perpetual movements.
Children of the universe.

Ong Ah Ung
Berdaya dan berdata untuk bergerak.
